    <h1 style="color: #00ffff;">Privacy Policy – Beat The Tower</h1>

    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> October 16, 2025</p>

    <p><em>Beat The Tower</em> does not collect, store, or share any personal data from its users.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #00ffff;">1. No Data Collection</h2>
    <p>The app does not collect any personal information, analytics, or identifiers. All gameplay data (such as your score or progress) remains entirely on your device and is never transmitted to any external server.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #00ffff;">2. No Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>The app does not use third-party analytics, advertising networks, or social media integrations that could track or identify users.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #00ffff;">3. Offline Use</h2>
    <p><em>Beat The Tower</em> can be played fully offline. No internet connection is required for gameplay.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #00ffff;">4. Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact the developer at:</p>
    <p><a href="mailto:gabrielemonte.mi@gmail.com" style="color: #00ffff;">gabrielemonte.mi@gmail.com</a></p>

    <p>By using the app, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.</p>

